>Not the most viable right now. 

And it has...when? Other than cheesy kill lanes I really don't see how this is bad in any way for variety. 

This can really help out some supports like {{champion:37}} {{champion:117}} {{champion:143}} {{champion:43}} {{champion:267}}

> This sounds mean but all you're telling me is that Zeke's Herald should stay an extremely niche item so people who don't want to take the time to learn about the ADC role can play a few kill lanes.

I'd hardly say "few kill lanes" really, I only mentioned the ones I commonly use. There are more kill lane candidates than there are ADCs.

{{champion:80}} {{champion:23}} {{champion:157}} {{champion:53}} {{champion:122}} {{champion:114}} {{champion:39}} {{champion:92}} {{champion:121}} {{champion:24}} {{champion:106}} {{champion:2}} {{champion:14}} {{champion:58}} {{champion:91}} {{champion:62}} 

Are some more valid kill laners bot that I do not use. Removing Zeke's takes from their potential in such a team composition.

I apologize I wasn't clear, I edited my response a short while after posting to mention that I welcome the new item; I just wish for the old item to stay as well. Perhaps give the new item a new name? The black dong for example ? {{item:3599}}
